dct_title_s: Map of the Ohio portion of the Wabash River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Wabash River Basin
dct_description_sm: Scale bar lower left corner of map.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
